        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme-component &amp;quot;AYUSH for Sports Medicine&amp;quot; under the &amp;quot;Ayurswasthya Yojana&amp;quot; by the Ministry of Ayush, Government of India, aims to provide AYUSH-based treatment and rehabilitation services to sports persons. AYUSH Sports medicine is a unique concept where, the treatment will be provided on sports injuries and promote the health and fitness of sports persons through AYUSH intervention. Fit India Movement is a nation-wide movement in India to encourage people to remain healthy and fit by including physical activities and sports in their daily lives. \n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "> **Financial Assistance:**\n\n\n  - Maximum grant of ₹1,00,00,000/- for one project for 18 months.\n  - The funds will be released in two installments of 60% and 40% of the total amount sanctioned. The second installment will be released after receiving expenditure of at least 75% of the released amount and after acceptance of UC thereof.\n\n<br>\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme-component aims to promote AYUSH interventions for the treatment and rehabilitation of sports injuries and to enhance health and fitness among sports persons.",
        "detailedDescription": [
          {
            "type": "align_justify",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The scheme-component \"AYUSH for Sports Medicine\" under the \"Ayurswasthya Yojana\" by the Ministry of Ayush, Government of India, aims to provide AYUSH-based treatment and rehabilitation services to sports persons. AYUSH Sports medicine is a unique concept where, the treatment will be provided on sports injuries and promote the health and fitness of sports persons through AYUSH intervention. Fit India Movement is a nation-wide movement in India to encourage people to remain healthy and fit by including physical activities and sports in their daily lives. "
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
