          "process_md": "&gt; **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Ayush NGO Portal](https://ngo.ayush.gov.in/register).\n**Step 2:** Fill in all the mandatory details and upload the relevant documents.\n**Step 3:** Verify the captcha and click on &amp;quot;Register&amp;quot;. If required, click &amp;quot;Cancel&amp;quot; to discard changes.\n&gt; **Login Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Ayush NGO Portal](https://ngo.ayush.gov.in/login).\n**Step 2:** Enter the registered email id, password. \n**Step 3:** Type the captcha and click on &amp;quot;Login&amp;quot;.\n\n  - User Manual: [Click here](https://ngo.ayush.gov.in/uploads/assets/Frontend_User_Manual_v-1.2.pdf).  - Contact Us: [Click here](https://ngo.ayush.gov.in/contact-us).\n<br>\n\n"
